    "description": {
      "value": "<div class=\"rd__b  rd__b--3\"><p>You channel primal magic to cause your teeth or fingernails to sharpen, ready to deliver a corrosive attack. Make a melee spell attack against one creature within 5 feet of you. On a hit, the target takes [[/damage 1d10 type=acid]] damage. After you make the attack, your teeth or fingernails return to normal.</p><p>The spell's damage increases by [[/damage 1d10]] when you reach 5th level ([[/damage 2d10]]), 11th level ([[/damage 3d10]]), and 17th level ([[/damage 4d10]]).</p></div>",
